Product name: Extremely Rare Deutschland tag 1996 Peace Beanie Baby, #4053 with many Errors! NW Toy, Mint condition with Mint Tags! Collectible bear
Description:
Extremly Rare Deutschland tag 1996 "PEACE BEAR" #4053 with many Errors!
Hello, 
If you are a serious collector you already know this original Ty bear is a rare collectors item! Gorgeous bear with multiple colors, and soft clean fabric.
* Hang tag is attached and is in great condition.
* This Brand New TY Beanie Baby is approx: 8" long. 
This bear has never been played with, and has been kept inside a ziploc bag, and is in mint condition!  
* FROM a NON - SMOKE Home !
A one of a kind Beanie Baby collectable.  
Some assets that attribute to the rarity of this bear include:
● The Ty address listed on the left interior of the hang tag - the "Fareham, Hants" is collectible and a rarity. 
● Missing "UK" after "5TX"
● Another Rare address. 
The third Ty address on the swing tag should say:
"Ty Canada 
Aurora, Ontario"
- This one says:
Ty Deutschland 
90008 Nürnberg 
● Original PVC pellets which newer models do NOT have.
● With no stamp on the inside of the tush tag, which indicates early manufacturing. (very rare). 
● The tush tag has both the "circle R" & "TM"
- On the hang tag says:
● "Peace" is in bold type.
With style #4053
● Date of birth should say, "February 1, 1996". This one says "2-1-96"
● Space between the Date of Birth and " : "
● No space between the last word "abound" and " ! "
- Free shipping!!
- Feel free to ask me any questions you have or if you need any additional photos. Thanks!
----- Similar Peace Beanie Baby with less errors and very common Canadian one, goes for sale on Ebay for 25,000.00 !
----- Serious byers only please! 
or BEST OFFER! 
Sincerely, 
Olha

Product name: Mid Century Suitcase Set // Vintage Avocado Green Retro Mod Luggage Set of Three Hard Shell Suitcases with Gold Interiors Storage Travel
Description:
In a retro avocado green, this is a vintage set of three mid-century suitcases. Each has a green plastic/rubber handle with silver latches and a gold vinyl interior. The smallest case has a mirror inset in the lid. No keys are included. Theses cases nest neatly inside one another for easy storage.

The case has a fair amount of scuffs and light stains on the exterior with some chew marks along one of the edges (see closeup). The latches and hinges have some light rusty tarnish. The other cases have some light exterior wear -- a few small stains and some little scuffed patches. The interiors are all in pretty good shape with a yellowed stain and small tear inside the large case (see closeup) and a slightly detached section inside the medium case.

Product name: Mid Century Home-made Camping Kitchen - Camping Chest - Portable Table "Lots of Character"
Description:
WOODEN CAMP KITCHEN - TRUNK - CHUCK BOX
We acquired this unique, home-made camp kitchen from a women who owned it told us her husband built it in the early 1960s. She said it was used extensively by their family on their camping adventures for many, many years. This cleverly designed cabinet measures 23.5" X 15" X 23" tall and the sides fold up to make a 48" X 23.5" table/work surface. It is constructed out of 1/2" plywood with aluminum edge guards on top and table top edges. The table leafs are held in place by two wooden dowels. Inside there are five compartments (shelves) in the main compartment and there is a 5" tall compartment underneath with flaps on each side--perfect for storing camp stove and fuel (the table dowels are also stored in the bottom hatch). All the flaps and sides are secured for transport with flip latches and there are thick rope handles on each end for carrying (weighs approx. 30 lbs.) The exterior has distressed red paint while the interior shelving has its original clear varnish. The rope handles are glued and stapled to the interior walls (you can see in last photo). This old piece has still has some life left in it for the vintage camper but would also make for a unique side table, bar, porch table, etc. NOTE- the chairs and/or props in the main photo are not included.
CONDITION:
This piece is structurally sound but has some distressing from over fifty years of service and storage. The red exterior paint is chippy and worn revealing some white paint and wood underneath. The plywood has some chips and fatigue mainly along the bottom edges. The metal latches has rust and pitting but still operate. The piano hinges on the table top leafs and bottom hatches have some rust and pitting as well but all still operate. The interior vanish is fairly clean but the original varnish is worn and there as some stains and a few remnants of paper in spots. 
SHIPPING:
Flat shipping rate of 49.95 to anywhere in the lower 48 USA states. It will probably ship via FedEx Ground so please provide a physical shipping address if different than your mailing address (no PO Boxes). We can also ship it to Alaska/Hawaii/US Territoriess but it will run a little more for shipping by USPS Parcel--Convo us for a shipping rate prior to purchasing for those locations. 
If you like this piece, you might also check out this vintage picnic case:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/492450133
STORE POLICIES NOTE:
When you purchase this item you are agreeing to our store policies. Please take a moment to review them.

Product name: ANTIQUE VICTORIAN sterling love token COIN bangle bracelet
Description:
This bracelet has it all. In original antique condition. The entire bracelet is coin sterling silver. The coins are seated Liberty coins from the 1800's. These coins were called Love Tokens.  They polished off the design of the coin and engraved their own message and design.  One coin is engraved 1888, one is engraved Grace, one is engraved with a monogram B, one is engraved Vinnie, one is engraved SC, one is engraved 1891, one is engraved ML, one is engraved Agnes, and the final one is engraved Ava.  Three are engraved on both sides.  
The coins are all worn smooth with age but the designs are all visible.  The loops are all welded on.    A rare find with 10 coins.  
The inside measurement of the piece is an adjustable 6" to 7 1/2" inches.

Product name: Rare Vintage Lucite Purse With Rhinestones By Patricia Of Miami
Description:
Rare Vintage Lucite Purse With Rhinestones Made in the 50's By Patricia Of Miami. 
In the late 1940s, various New York handbag companies released lines of Lucite purses. 
By 1950, Miami Beach had become the happening spot for wealthy American vacationers; its fun-in-the-sun, holiday appeal made it the perfect spot to sell Lucite purses. Many Florida-based manufacturers sprung up in the early ‘50s one of them was, Patricia of Miami.
This purse has a very unique design. The color is a mix of beige black and dark green. 
The lucite is in excellent condition. However , this purse has lost some of its rhinestones over the years.

Product name: Hummel 47 / 3 / 0 Goose Girl - TMK 2 - 4 inch - Goebel Hummel Figurine - Goebel Figurine - Girl Hummel Collectible Figurine - Trademark 2
Description:
Hummel Figurine #47/3/0 "Goose Girl" 
4 inch tall TMK 2 (trademark 2 full bee)
Good condition.  
These Goebel collectibles have been lovingly cared for by my mother and grandmother who began collecting them in the late 1940's.
My uncle, stationed in Germany as part of the U.S. occupational forces at the close of WWII, discovered the lovely porcelain figurines created by the W. Goebel company based on the drawings of M.I. Hummel.
Knowing his sister and mother loved dolls, he mailed some back to them as gifts and ,thus began their life-long love affair with Hummels.
They continued to add to and enlarge their collection throughout the rest of their lives.

Description:
This antique Music Box was purchased over forty years ago by myself and is in excellent condition. It was manufactured before 1886 but I do not know the exact date.

Product name: Unique Art 3D Art Avant Garde Artwork Rad Painted Rock Blue Art Collectibles Stylish Aristocratic Gift for Him Awesome Luxury Gift for Her
Description:
Magnificent avant garde original art in blues, brown, and charcoal. This abstract art is signed dated and numbered artwork. 3D art is a stunning conversation piece that makes a fantastic statement for home decor or office decor. This aristocratic blue artwork is a collectible stone art unique gift for him or a radical luxury gift for her. This awesome unique art is an awesome hand painted rock that would be a fabulous statement gift for husband. This spectacular one of a kind three dimensional art is the perfect gift for someone who has everything.  
This is Ishi Stone #13, of the Streamers series. It has the natural stone background, forming some of the "streamers", with the remainder of the streamers colored dark blue, turquoise, brown, and charcoal. There is a satin finish, blue band. The Stone is signed, numbered, and dated by me, artist Delores Malcomson. I sign my work "DMIshi" (DM are my initials, and the word" Ishi" means rock or stone, in Japanese), with the copyright symbol, the date, and the code for the name of the design, in this case "ST" for Streamers, and 13 for the number of the stone. The medium is acrylic paint, and satin acrylic varnish to seal the stone. This Ishi is, approximately, 3" wide x 5 & 1/2" long x 4" at its' highest. It is self standing. The stone can be rotated in different directions to present a variety of faces, as your mood dictates. The photographs show the front side and the back side, of the stone, in the different positions that you can display it. This is OOAK, One-of-a-Kind, you will own the only one.
UNFAMILIAR WITH ISHI STONES? READ THE DESCRIPTION, BELOW:
Ishi Stones are common river and beach stones that have been transformed into works of fine art, by me, artist Delores Malcomson. Each Ishi Stone is signed, numbered, and dated by me. I work my designs all around the stones, enveloping them, incorporatating the stone and design together into multifaceted, 3 dimensional artworks. The whole of the design is not seen immediately, but is discovered as the stone is turned and viewed from different angles. The Stone can be rotated in different directions to present a variety of faces, as your mood dictates. The photographs show the front side and the back side, of the Stone, in the different positions that you can display it.
I have taken the art of painting on stone to a new level, with my original designs and color finishes. In the spirit of traditional Japanese art, Impressed by the fact that simplicity and essence of nature, combined with the elaborate are always reflected in Japanese art, the name of "Ishi" (which translates stone or rock, in Japanese) was chosen to represent my work. The challenge of taking an object, that is generally considered to be of little interest or value, and turning it into a work of art is what inspires me to bring life and beauty to an otherwise ignored element of nature.
See more unique artwork by checking out my Ishi Gallery, at: 
http://www.ishigallery.etsy.com
 You will see OOAK hand painted rocks, gourds, and boxes, Limited Edition Photographs, note cards, coffee mugs, mouse pads, calendars, t-shirts, and tote bags.

Product name: Extremely Rare- 4 Vintage One Of A Kind Dog Booties worn in the Famous Alaska Iditarod Race
Description:
Vintage Dog Booties worn in the Iditarod Race!   Great Christmas gifts!  Very limited quantity.
These dog booties were worn by actual Iditarod Dogs racing to Nome, AK between 1990-2000
ONE OF A KIND ! Special friends of mine were part of the Follow Up Team.  They were responsible for making sure of the position of each team at night so no Team was left behind.  Their job was very important making sure that all the mushers and their teams were safe.  After 25 years my friends retired, therefore, the supply of booties has stopped.
You won't find these authentic Iditarod Dog Booties anywhere else!  Because of the rarity of these booties when they are sold out, unfortunately there won't be any more. 
Make your dog an Iditarod Dog!!
About the Iditarod:
The Iditarod is 1049 miles of the roughest, most beautiful terrain Mother Nature has to offer. She throws jagged mountain ranges, frozen river, dense forest, desolate tundra and miles of windswept coast at the mushers and their dog teams. Add to that temperatures far below zero, winds & hazards of overflow, long hours of darkness and treacherous climbs and side hills, and you have the Iditarod. A race extraordinaire, a race to save lives!
From Anchorage, in south central Alaska, to Nome on the western Bering Sea coast.
It’s not just a sled dog race, it’s a race in which unique men and woman compete. Mushers enter from all walks of life. Fishermen, lawyers, doctors, miners, artists, natives, Canadians, Swiss, French and others.  Men and women each with their own story, each with their own reasons for going the distance. Hundreds  of volunteers, men and women, students and village residents all help to organize and stage the event. They man headquarters at Wasilla, Anchorage, and Nome.  They fly volunteers, veterinarians, dog food and supplies. They act as checkers, coordinators, and family supporters of each musher.

Product name: BEST SELLING! Tiki Rope perches / parrot swings - 4' length x 1.5" diameter. Outstanding toys for cockatoos, African Greys, Amazons, conures
Description:
Natural Manila Rope   
Non-toxic / Not treated      
304 Stainless steel Hardware
Indoor / Outdoor 
Long Lasting
Great for Pluckers
High Quality
Our parrot ropes are natural non-toxic manila and have stainless steel hardware to eliminate the danger of heavy metal toxicity and rusting.  They can be used indoors in cages or outdoors in aviaries, between play gyms, from the ceiling as a play area, or hung vertically or diagonal for enriching environmental variety!  The ropes are very durable, lasting well with daily use from large macaws and cockatoos and are used in zoos and aviaries across the country.  The manila is a brittle fiber rope, similar to sisal but with a much softer more natural texture, so toe nails do not get tangled in the fibers like cotton.  It needs very little trimming, if any, over the life of the rope.  This makes them a favorite for use in breeder cages and aviaries as the birds can enjoy rope perches without the need for constant intrusion from their caretakers.  They are also excellent for birds with plucking issues as they love to preen the fibers of the rope.  This holds true for the smaller birds as well - including cockatiels, budgies, poicephalus, psittacula (asiatic parakeets), african greys, amazons, conures, and australian grass parakeets.  We have received an amazing amount of feedback from our eclectus and cockatiel owners telling us how much their birds love picking at the fibers of these ropes!  For our African Greys, we recommend the larger 2" diameter as they seem to enjoy the stability of the perch to the smaller, less rigid 1.5" ropes.  And, of course, these are customer favorites for those who share their lives with the large macaws and cockatoos.  Read our Customer Reviews for more feedback about these best sellers.
Please allow for slight variations to the length of the rope as we hand make each one.  Clean with warm water and grape seed extract; dry in the sun. 
The Tiki Ropes comes in Two diameters - 1.5" and 2"
The 1 1/2 inch rope is appropriate for all birds from budgies to large macaws and cockatoos.  To maintain healthy feet and add enrichment, it is beneficial to offer a variety of perch sizes in your parrot's cage and environment.  Observations of wild birds including parakeets, lories, pionus, conures, cockatoos, and macaws show that they comfortably perch on a wide variety of diameters and surfaces from very thick, fat, tree branches where their feet sit almost flat to teeny, tiny, twigs that can barely hold their weight.  So don't be afraid to 'branch out' from the "recommended" perch sizes!  However, from extensive observations of our own parrots on their ropes for the past decade, we can tell you that they like "the big ones!"  It appears that they enjoy an "oversize" rope to one that is similar in size to their usual perches.  This holds true for the little birds as well.  The cockatiels prefer their big 1 1/2 inch rope to their 1/2" rope, two feathers down!     The medium sized birds can go either way - 1 1/2 inch or 2 inch.  This includes amazons, african Greys, eclectus, small cockatoos, and mini macaws.  However, when given the choice, many African Greys choose the 2 inch rope, as it is more stable and supportive.  My goffins cockatoo, Halo, also prefers the larger 2" rope over the 1.5" size.  Our definite recommendations for the large macaws and cockatoos are the 2 inch rope.  These big birds LOVE big ropes.  If you have a Moluccan or Umbrella, get ready for some serious flapping fun!

Product name: Bulbasaur Planter - Aurora Blue - Pokemon
Description:
***Update (2/22): The old size is now listed as Small, and the new size will be Medium. The small Bulbasaur has a potting space of about 1.6" diameter and .9" depth which makes it only suitable for very small succulents or seedlings. The medium Bulbasaur has a potting space of about 1.9" diameter and 1.1" depth which is a lot more than it sounds (I'll post a picture soon). Processing time is 3 days.***
Introducing the Aurora Blue Bulbasaur. We came up with a new 3D printing technique which combines colors in a way that's never been done before. We call the technique "Jelly Donut" and this Bulbasaur is the result.
"Jelly Donut" - A New Way for Printing Two Colors
We wanted to use Bulbasaur's original colors, but mix them in a way that only 3D printing can. We carefully printed the outer shell in green and the inner structure in blue. Both colors are translucent allowing them to blend naturally as light passes through. Shining brilliantly when viewed at various angles, the luster surface is a nod to the holographic rare cards. With its soft blend of blue green hues and reflected highlights, this Bulbasaur is our tribute to a beloved Pokemon.
Based on our market research surveys, we determined this size, 2.8" length by 2.6" width by 2.4" height, to be the optimal balance of practicality and cuteness factor.
This technique maintains complete functionality like all other Bulbasaur planters: simply place a small succulent on his back.
Thank you to LeoDuhVinci whose original design can be found here:

Description:
We make our premium fish tanks out of premium USA-Sourced Cell-cast Acrylic Material. This results in an edge-less design where the entire tank is perfectly clear. This material is scratch resistant and offers better optical clarity and lowers optical distortion than glass. 
Our tanks are diamond cut and the edges are polished to a mirror finish. They are structurally secure and the sides will not bow due to water pressure.
This tank is 40" Long, 12" Deep, and 12" Tall; 1/2" Thick. It is 5-sided with an open top. A sump or other structures can be added as required. It is approx. 24 Gallons in volume.
Acrylic Fish Tanks are 17x stronger, softer and more flexible than glass as well as far more impact resistant. Unlike glass, acrylic adds no color tint.
We are able to make tanks in any size/dimensions you may require, so be sure to ask us if you need a custom size!

Description:
►EpicDiamonds◄
Claddagh Engagement Unique Ring with Natural pink Morganite  
The Claddagh ring (Irish: fainne Chladaigh) is a traditional Irish ring given which represents love, loyalty,
and friendship (the hands represent friendship, the heart represents love, and the crown represents loyalty).
The design and customs associated with it originated in the Irish fishing village of Claddagh.The ring, as currently known, was first produced in the 17th century.
It's been re-created  with a beautiful natural pink Morganite at the heart(can be created with Blue,White Sapphire or Diamond).
It's available in your choice of 14K  White, Yellow  or Rose Gold.

Description:
CHRISTMAS MEMORY BOOK
Record the next 10 years of Christmases in ONE book! 
This unique book features delightful graphic designs commemorating the next ten years, perfectly bound in a 12" x 9" matte finish, hard cover. Each year offers a two-page spread for you to add your own photo prints and write down your memories in the spaces, "How we spent our Christmas," and "Special Moments". You won't find anything else like this out there! Limited quantities available!

Product name: EOSTRE
Description:
EOSTRE (WEDDING COLLECTION). Just for unconventional weddings: different brides, unique wedding corsets
ENG: SINGLE MADE JUST FOR YOU: Once you order it, we'll put us in contact with you to ensure you give us the correct and accurate measures, so that we can do the perfect corset for you and your unique body.
This Overbust Corset is ideal for a wedding, or just changing the colors, a unique, luxury and elegant corset for any especial occasion. It is made with satind, lining with organza, and flowers of lace brocade, fixed one by one in the corset.  It has a heartshaped bustline. It has a cut over the hip, which accentuates even more the female curves in the well known nineteenth-century-figure named after "hourglass". 
It is made with four layers of fabric, fully armed with steel spiral bones. The front and back of the corset have flat bones, which will reduce and constraint even more. The bones are coated with gross grain to give more durability and make it comfortable. It has also a waist reduction tape inside and a steel boned Modesty Panel or back panel. And, of course, satin interlining.
For any other modification, (for example, if you want it without busk) other colour or materials that are not listed in the tabs, do not hesitate to contact and ask us.

Product name: Vintage 1940's 2 Piece Wedding Outfit, Alfred Angelo Designer Bridal Outfit, Vintage Bridal Suit, Forest, Fairytale, 40's Wedding Suit
Description:
********** Vintage Evening Dresses **********
In the Edwardian era, women's day dresses and evening gowns had an S-curve silhouette. During the 1920s, the hems rose and decorations became more showy. This would lead to more conservative dresses during the Great Depression. After the end of World War II, in 1947, Christian Dior introduced his "New Look" of nipped-in waistlines and full skirts. Luxurious fabrics were used for these dresses, and the ball gown was re-introduced. The ball gown often has a strapless bodice, although short and long sleeves are common as long as the cut is off-the-shoulder. Ball gowns remain the most formal female attire to this day, and are worn exclusively to balls.
Florence Lace carefully selects and sources vintage evening gowns for ladies who want to create the above and for those who love feminine, elegant and delicately made dresses. Some of our dresses are vintage and have been previously owned so may have minor indications of their former life. These will be described as accurately as is possible, will be photographed and will be made available upon request. The photographs are an important part of the description and indicate the item you will receive, so please look at the photographs and read the description carefully. 
We also have a range of brand new vintage styled elegant dresses. Please view the following link : https://www.freewebstore.org/florence-lace
(ref D-086) 
********** The designer **********
 ALFRED ANGELO, established since 1934 in the USA is a highly acclaimed Bridal shop and is now one of the world's largest manufacturers and retailers of wedding dresses. The company is headquartered in Delray Beach, Florida. While Alfred Angelo is most recognised for its wedding dress fashions, the company also designs bridesmaid dresses, fashions for the mother of the bride, flower girl dresses, and wedding accessories. In 2014, Alfred Angelo celebrated 80 years of dressing brides and is best known for classic designs, while continuing to set new bridal trends.
********** Description **********
This outfit is from Alfred Angelo's modern does vintage collection and is a stunning 2 Piece wedding outfit made in the 1980's, in the style of the 40's, from ivory chiffon. The outfit is fully lined and consists of a long-sleeved jacket style top and long skirt. 
The top of the outfit is long sleeved and gives the appearance of a jacket. It features a modern yet classy and elegant chic satin collar neckline that shapes into the body and wraps over to one side with 2 lovely bows. It has a concealed zip at the back of the top and lovely satin cuffs. 
The A line skirt flows to the floor and has a flattering split to the front and side. This is a high quality piece and the ILGWU label is a mark of its quality and authenticates the outfit to be vintage. 
This outfit designed as a wedding/bridal outfit or a Mother of the Bride outfit and would be perfect for a forest, pagan, fairy tale wedding, a causal wedding on the beach an intimate evening event at a banquet hall or a 40's wedding. It could be worn to a Formal event, red carpet or a special occasion, such as a Christening etc. 
Look at the photographs and you will see how beautiful this 2 piece is together and although the dress is vintage, it is in a VERY GOOD condition.
The dress is approx size 14/16 but please check the measurements carefully before purchase and contact by email (message to sender) if you have any queries or questions. 
40'' bust 
32'' waist 
38'' skirt length 
26'' jacket top length from shoulder to hem  
********** Colour Resolution **********
We cannot guarantee a precise colour (computer monitors may have slight variations on colour, so the colour you see via computer may differ slightly from the "real thing"; especially gold colour items)
********** Shipping**********
We do ship worldwide but as some destinations come under different shipping zones please email us for a quote. We do combine postage for multiple purchases but the total will be dependent on weight so please contact us for a postage quote.
All items are insured and tracked and you will receive a tracking number once your items have been dispatched. 
********** Thank you for visiting and for shopping at Florence Lace *********

Product name: Dragon Corset
Description:
Hand dyed silk with organza 'scales' and hand dyed silk lining. This can be made available in a choice of colours as the silk is custom dyed. Wide steel busk front opening with black metal hook closure. Modesty panel and satin ribbon laced eyelets at the back. 
Matching fabric based accessories can be made available at an additional time and cost.  
Matching skirts and bridal wear can also be made available at an additional time and cost. 
All my couture corsets contain an internal waist stay which reinforces the area for gentle waist reduction of 2" - 4", depending on how 'squishy' you are, and are constructed from the finest spiral and sprung steel boning and English cotton coutil to support, smooth, define and enhance your figure into an hourglass shape. It is only the waist area that should be cinched, the bust should not be squeezed or flattened.
All my front opening corsets have finest quality wide steel busks to further smooth the silhouette. Choose from traditional hooks and eyes or dramatic swing hooks, available in a choice of colours. If the corset has a closed front this area is re-enforced with multiple sprung steels to act in the same smoothing way.
Full length eyelet lacing to the back ensures that the waist can be comfortably pulled in. Eyelets are also available in a choice of colours. I have also learned as the years have passed that a modesty panel is a must to avoid the view of squeezed flesh behind the laces. This ensures that you look beautiful from the back as well as the front. I prefer to use high quality double sided satin ribbon for lacing for a luxurious, glamorous finish to the back of the corset. It will also preserve your hands when tightening!
All patterns and designs are drafted by myself and are the property and copyright of Powdered and Waisted Corsetry. 
All images are the property and copyright of Powdered and Waisted Corsetry and may not be reproduced without permission.
Model: Ivy Tenebrae
For ease of ordering, my corset sizes are based on UK dress sizes. Please supply this and your natural waist, bust, hip and height measurements when first contacting me to discuss your requirements and place an order. 
Overseas clients, please contact me for an accurate postage quote as depending where you are and how it's packaged and sent to you can make a big difference to the postage price!
Thanks for looking.

Description:
FiberFeltNMore is not only your trusted source for fiber arts, but we are also a trusted name in wool crafting supply.  This listing is for wool roving by the pound.
This white wool top is 29.5 micron with average color and 2-3 inch bulk staple.  This white wool roving is a standard type that traditionally was used in medium knitting yarns and is a primary export from the United States today.  We are proud to share our wool roving for sale, and all knitting yarn wool is collected from small farms in the Fleece State area of the United States.  
For those of you not familiar with the Fleece State, this includes all states east of the Mississippi and any state west that is not split off by the Continental Divide.  
When purchasing your knitting supplies from us, please remember that this wool crafting supply is sold by the pound and plan your order accordingly.

Product name: Milk Kefir Grains (2 heaping Tbsp)
Description:
Kefir is a fermented drink. It has a consistency that is between milk and yogurt. These kefir grains can be used in almost any type of milk (we put ours in whole milk). One heaping tablespoon of kefir grains in a quart jar of milk makes set kefir in 24-48 hours. Kefir has many strains of good bacteria and probiotics that colonize your digestive tract. Kefir also contains a more digestible form of calcium than milk. The kefir grains eat the lactose out of the milk, so kefir is virtually lactose free. 
To ship we double bag 2 heaping tablespoons of milk kefir grains with a little milk (so the grains don't starve in transit) in BPA free zip-lock bags. We will also include instructions on how to begin making kefir with your grains. To ensure that your kefir grains arrive quickly and alive, we only ship with USPS priority mail.

The anodized colours of niobium are rich, saturated and bright.

*Niobium is as hypo-allergenic as pure gold so these earrings can be worn by anyone and everyone. It is about 20% lighter than sterling silver and less than half the weight of gold.

Product name: Leather Wingtip Shoes, Mens Wingtip Shoes, Black Formal Shoes, Black Brogue Shoes, Leather Wingtip Shoes, Custom Leather Shoes.
Description:
Traditional brogue shoes design One of the most used classic shoe design in the world. 
These shoes are totally handcrafted and made from premium quality naked cowhide leather. All natural leather with full grain texture of the skin; a true sign for high quality leather.
These shoes are fully leather lined with compressed double leather sole throughout hand stitched and hand finished.
These brogues are made following Goodyear welted construction. A generations old technique which allows shoes maker to resole the shoes without disturbing the upper of the leather. This allows the shoes to last even more longer.
The toe shape of these shoes are conventional round which makes them a true classic design and more comfortable as they provide more room for your feet. 
All the brogue punches are individually hand punched by expert upper maker to make brogue pattern.
These shoes are good for formal wearing as well as casual wearing with jeans.

Description:

About Bramble… 
Office employee by day.

Daydreamer by necessity.

2. date ( you want us to personalize the tags with)

Less smooth and looks a tag unfinished but that is just the texture of the leather. We can customize the back with anything that you want. Sometimes we dye the back a bit lighter so the text is more visible. 
Please include any information you want on the back of the tag during check out. We will not confirm your information. We will just cut, paste, and then engrave ( so please double check). 
COORDINATE LOOK UP INFORMATION  -

http://www.latlong.net
THIS LISTING INCLUDES the text format you see pictured….
 If you want a different quote than you need to purchase a the  listing below and we can create a custom tag for you

Buy the link below if you require a more specific customization. 
( if you are reading this during the busy months ( christmas or wedding season) this option most likely will not be available. 
Link to Buy if you need a more personalized tag with a greater font selection: 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/452367520/personalized-leather-luggage-tag-genuine?ref=shop_home_active_1
GIVE US YOUR PERSONALIZATION IN THE NOTES TO SELLER BOX : 
FRONT : coordinates and date
Back : whatever you want on the back. People generally do name, number, and email. 
Luggage Tag Specs.
1. All our tags are made by hand ( in my workshop). We are located in the United States. 
2. Both sides can be personalized. The back of the tag is not as smooth and a bit more rustic looking. Please look at picture number two and make sure that you like the look because it cant be changed.  
3. Hardware is provided 
4.  Measures 3.5 " long x 2 " wide. 
5.  Color is saddle brown but may vary slightly from picture. All of our tags are hand dyed so please allow for variation.
                          IMPORTANT BRAMBE FACTS                             
1. We can engrave any quote that you want. There are no character or word limits. 
2. We do not STAMP or Letterpress our customizations. Our personalizations are burned into the leather. This means that your quote will not disappear or wear down.
3. We can also do any font size but we have a set formula that we tend to use as a guide. Sometimes the size font that you may like might not translate well.. Meaning the font could look quite large on your computer screen but will actually look small on the surface of the leather. 
4. Double check the information you give us for your personalization. We will simply cut and paste your note. If it is incorrect or misspelled that will be what you see on your passport. So please take a couple of minutes and read your quote out loud ( to yourself) to make sure there are no mistakes.
5. Sometimes the leather may have a nick or a slight dye imperfection. This is because we hand make all of our items. It is not considered a flaw. We just don't produce assembly line things. We process all of our leather and try to use every possible part. 
We are starting to list full hides. So if you are looking for something hide oriented send us a note.
